hadiths[15]{hadithnumber,text}:
6708,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qareeb ho ja , main qareeb hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tumharey sar ke kapdey takleef de rahe hain? maine arz kya, ji haan , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir rozey sadqa ya qurbani ka fidya dedey aur mujhey Ibne-Aun ne khabar di, unse Ayub ne bayan kya ke rozey teen din ke hongey aur qurbani aik bakri ki aur) khaney ke liye) chh miskeen hongey."
6709,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya, main to tabah ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat hai? arz kya ke maine Ramazan main apni biwi se ham-bistarii kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya tum aik ghulam aazad kar saktey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya 2 mahiney mutwaatir rozey rakh sakta hai. unhon-ne arz kya ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya sath miskinon ko khana khilaa sakta hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke baith jao wo sahib baith gaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik tokraa laya gaya jis mein khajoorein thin ( arq ( aik bada paimaana hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ley ja aur usey pura sadqa kar de. unhon-ne poochha, kya apne se zyada mohtaaj par) sadqa kar doon)? is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans diye aur aap ke samney ke daant Mubarak dikhai dene lagey aur phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne bachchon hi ko khilaa dena."
6710,"aik sahib Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz ki, main to tabah ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya baat hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Ramazan main apni biwi se sohbat kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke koi ghulam hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. malum farmaya mutwaatir 2 mahiney rozey rakh saktey ho, unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. malum farmaya sath miskinon ko khana khilaa saktey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir aik Ansari sahabi ( arq ( lekar hazir huey, ( arq ( aik paimaana hai, usmein khajoorein thin, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ley ja aur sadqa kar de. unhon-ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kya main apne se zyada zarurat mand par sadqa karun? us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai. un donon maidaanon ke darmyan koi gharaana ham se zyada mohtaaj nahi hai phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ja aur apne ghar walon hi ko khilaa de."
6711,"eik sahib Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz ki, main to tabah ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya baat hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Ramazan main apni biwi se sohbat kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke koi ghulam hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. malum farmaya mutwaatir 2 mahiney rozey rakh saktey ho, unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. malum farmaya sath miskinon ko khana khilaa saktey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir aik Ansari sahabi ( arq ( lekar hazir huey, ( arq ( aik paimaana hai, usmein khajoorein thin, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ley ja aur sadqa kar de. unhon-ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kya main apne se zyada zarurat mand par sadqa karun? us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai. un donon maidaanon ke darmyan koi gharaana ham se zyada mohtaaj nahi hai phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ja aur apne ghar walon hi ko khilaa de."
6712,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein aik saa tumharey zamane ke mudd se aik mudd aur tehai ke barabar hota tha. baad mein Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ke zamane mein usmein zyadti ki gaee.
6713,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Ramazan ka fitraana Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ke pahley mudd ke wazan se detey they aur qism ka kaffara bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mudd se hi detey they. abu-Qutaiba ne isi sanad se bayan kya ke ham se Imam Malik ne bayan kya ke hamara mudd tumharey mudd se bada hai aur hamarey nazdeek tarjeeh sirf Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ke mudd ko hai. aur mujh se Imam Malik ne bayan kya ke agar aisa koi Hakim aaya jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mudd se chhota mudd muqarrar kar de to tum kis hisab se ( sadqa fitr wghaira) nikah logey ? maine arz kya ke aisi sura mein ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ke mudd ke hisab se fitra nikala karengey ? unhon-ne kaha ke kya tum dekhtey nahi ke mamla hamesha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ke mudd ki taraf laut'taa hai.
6714,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Allah ! unke ( كيل ( paimaaney mein unke saa aur unke mudd mein barkat ata farmaa. ''
6715,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne kisi musalman ghulam ko aazad kya to Allah Taala uske eik-eik tukdey ke badley aazad karne waley ka eik-eik tukda jahannam se aazad karega. yahan tak ke ghulam ki sharmgah ke badley aazad karne waley ki sharmgah bhi dozakh se aazad ho jaaeygii.''
6716,qabila Ansar ke aik sahib ne apne ghulam ko mudabbir bana liya aur unke paas us ghulam ke siwa aur koi maal nahi tha. jab iski itlaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mili to aap ne malum farmaya ke mujh se is ghulam ko kon khareedtaa hai. Naeem bin nahaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne aath (8) so dirham main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usey khareed liya. maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna ke wo aik qibtii ghulam tha aur pahley saal mar gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey neelaam farma kar us raqam se usey mukammal aazad kara diya.
6717,"unhon-ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko (aazaad karne ke liye) khareednaa chaha, to unke pahley maalikon ne apne liye 'walaa' ki shart lagaaii. maine iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khareed lo, 'walaa' to usi se hoti hai jo aazad karta hai."
6718,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein qabila ash'ar ke chand logon ke sath hazir hua aur aap se sawari ke liye janwar maangey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism main tumhen sawari ke janwar nahi de sakta. phir jab tak Allah Taala ne chaha ham thahrey rahe aur jab kuchh oont aaey to teen oont hamein diye janey ka hukm farmaya, jab ham unhein lekar chaley to ham mein se kuchh ne apne sathiyon se kaha ke hamein Allah usmein barkat nahi dega. ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas sawari ke janwar maangney aaey they, to aap ne qism kha li thi ke hamein sawari ke janwar nahi de saktey aur aap ne inayat farmaai hain. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumharey liye janwar ka intizam nahi kya hai balke Allah Taala ne kya hai, Allah ki qism ! agar Allah ne chaha to jab bhi mein koi qism kha loonga aur phir iske siwa aur cheez mein achai hogi to main apni qism ka kaffara de doonga aur wahi kaam karunga jis mein achai hogi."
6719,main qism ka kaffara ada kar doonga aur wo kaam karunga jis mein achai hogi ya (is tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) main kaam wo karunga jis mein achai hogi aur kaffara ada kar doonga .
6720,"Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ne kaha tha ke aaj raat main apni nawwey beeviyon ke paas jaaunga aur har biwi aik bachcha janegi jo Allah ke rastey mein jihad karengey. unke sathi Sufiyan yani Farishtey ne unse kaha, ajii inshaAllah to kaho lekin aap bhool gaey aur phir tamam beeviyon ke paas gaey lekin aik biwi ke siwa jiske yahan adhooraa bachcha hua tha kisi biwi ke yahan bhi bachcha nahi hua. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey huey kehtey they ke agar unhon-ne inshaAllah keh diya hota to unki qism be-kaar na jati aur apni zarurat ko pa letey aur aik martaba unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha ke agar unhon-ne istisnaa (exception) kar diya hota aur ham se abu-Zinaad ne Aaraj se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
6721,"ham abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they aur hamarey qabila aur us qabila jurm mein bhaaii-chaargii aur aapas mein bhaley rawaiye ki ravish thi. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir khana laya gaya aur khaney mein murghi ka gosht bhi tha. rawi ne bayan kya ke haaziriin mein banii-Taimillaah ka aik shakhs surkh rang ka bhi tha jaisey Maula ho. bayan kya ke wo shakhs khaney par nahi aaya to Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha ke Sharik ho jao, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iska gosht khaatey dekha hai. us shakhs ne kaha ke maine usey gandagi khaatey dekha tha jab se us se ghin aaney lagi aur usi waqt maine qism kha li ke kabhi iska gosht nahi khaaunga. abu-Musa ne kaha : qareeb aao main tumhen iske mutaalliq bataunga . ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan ash-ariyon ki aik jamat ke sath aaey aur maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawari ka janwar maanga . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt sadqe ke oonton mein se taqseem kar rahe they. Ayub ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt ghussa they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism ! main tumhen sawari ke janwar nahi de sakta aur na mere paas koi aisi cheez hai jo sawari ke liye tumhen de sakun . bayan kya ke phir ham wapas aa gaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ghaneemat ke oont aaey, to puchha gaya ke ash-ariyon ki jamat kahan hai. ham hazir huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein panch umda oont diye janey ka hukm diya. bayan kya ke ham wahan se rawaana huey to maine apne sathiyon se kaha ke ham pahley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas sawari ke liye aaey they, to aap ne qism kha li thi ke sawari ka intizam nahi kar saktey. phir hamein bula bheja aur sawari ka janwar inayat farmaaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni qism bhool gaey hongey. Allah ki qism ! agar ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aap ki qism ke barey mein ghafalat mein rakha to ham kabhi kaamyaab nahi hongey. chalo ham sab aap ke paas wapas chalein aur aapko aap ki qism yad dilaaein . chunanche ham wapas aaey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! ham pahley aaey they aur aap se sawari ka janwar maanga tha to aap ne qism kha li thi ke aap iska intizam nahi kar saktey , ham ne samjha ke aap apni qism bhool gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao, tumhen Allah ne sawari di hai, Allah ki qism agar Allah ne chaha to main jab bhi koi qism kha loon aur phir dusri cheez ko uske muqabil behtar samjhoon to wahi karunga jo behtar hoga aur apni qism tod doonga. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ayub se ki, unse abu-Qilaba aur Qasim bin Aasim kaleebii ne."
6722,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' kabhi tum hukumat ka ohda talab na karna kyonke agar bila maangey tumhen ye mil jaeyga to usmein tumhari minjaab Allah madad ki jaeygi, lekin agar maangney par mila to Sara bojh tumheii par daal diya jaeyga aur agar tum koi qism kha lo aur uske siwa koi aur baat behtar nazar aaey to wahi karo jo behtar ho aur qism ka kaffara ada kar do. Usman bin umr ke sath is hadis ko ash'hal bin Hatim ne bhi Abdullah-bin Aun se riwayat kya, isko abu-Awana aur Hakim ne milayaa  aur Abdullah-bin Aun ke sath is hadis ko Yunus aur simaak bin Atiya aur simaak bin Harab aur Humaid aur Qatada aur Mansoor aur Hisham aur Rabe ne bhi riwayat kya."
